summary:
...LESLIE ACCELERATING NORTHEASTWARD AND SHOULD BECOME EXTRATROPICAL DURING THE NEXT COUPLE OF DAYS...
 As of 11:00 PM AST Fri Oct 11

 The minimum central pressure was 1001 mb
